title: [Western Harbor, Approach]
description: Thick blades of beach grass rise upon either side of the cobblestone pathway as it gently curves away from a large stone wall and down toward a quaint harbor.  Sunlight glitters off of the dark blue waters, where boats can be seen bobbing safely from their moorings.

Thick blades of beach grass rise upon either side of the cobblestone pathway as it gently curves away from a large stone wall and down toward a quaint harbor.  Pale moonlight glitters off of the dark blue waters, where shadowy objects can be seen bobbing up and down.
